  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting Social Accountability in Education sector in Lao Cai province, Vietnam</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will seek to address issues of accountability and local people&apos; participation in education governance through promoting education managers, teachers and parents to practice participatory processes of decision making, planning, budgeting, monitoring and evaluation and piloting channels for policy feedback or policy dialogues between these main actors in Lao Cai province. The project will contribute to increase the number of children and their representatives exercising their rights to have better accessibility to quality basic education</narrative>
  </description>
